Privacy Policy
This document applies to oCoder Apps, the mobile apps developed by Truong Xuan Trung. We've tried to keep text simple, so we hope you will take a time to read it carefully.
Personal information
We made apps with your privacy in mind, so we do not collect personally identifiable information about you. In other words, we do not collect information such as your name, address, phone number, email address or precise geographic location.
Advertising
We use ads to keep our apps free for you. All ads in our App served by Google's AdMob network or facebook Audience network. AdMob may use and collect anonymous data about your interests to customize advertising in our App and in other sites and apps. To do that AdMob using unique user-resettable Advertising ID, provided by Google Play services. Interest and location data may be linked to your device, but is not linked to your identity. To learn more about AdMob privacy policies and opt-out choices check out
Google's privacy policy
.
Changes
We will post any privacy policy changes on this page and, if the changes are significant, we will provide a more prominent notice. If you have any questions or concerns about our privacy policies, please use a contact form on this page.
